title: The MCU Comes to TV: A Guide to ‘WandaVision’
description:
After concluding their discussion of Part 2 of HBO’s Tiger Woods documentary series, Sean and Amanda dive back into the MCU by taking a close look at the first two episodes of Marvel’s first Disney+ series, ‘WandaVision.’ 

Hosts: Sean Fennessey and Amanda Dobbins
